NK132(no)007:1: // bar do'i smon lam dgongs gcig rgya mtsho'i 'bru 'grel gsal ba'i sgron me zhes bya ba bzhugs so ////
NK132(no)007:2: rigs kyi bdag po dpal ldan bla ma dam pa'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK132(no)007:3: de la 'dir bar do'i smon lam dgongs gcig rgya
NK132(no)007:4: mtsho zhes bya ba 'di nyid 'chad pa la don
NK132(no)007:5: bzhi ste / rang bzhin gyi bar do dang /
NK132(no)007:7: chos nyid kyi bar do dang /
NK132(no)007:8: rnam smin srid pa bar do dang bzhi las /
NK132(no)007:10: bla ma la gsol ba btab nas bcas rang gi
NK132(no)007:11: nyes ltung bshags sdom byed cing thugs dam gnad nas
NK132(no)007:12: bskul ba / de'i mthus skye gnas bar dor grol bar smon pa'o //
NK132(no)007:14: sngon byon sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa /
NK132(no)007:15: da lta'i sangs rgyas kyi rgyal tshab /
NK132(no)007:16: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi 'byung gnas
NK132(no)007:17: yin pas na dus gsuma sangas rgyas thams cad kyi
NK132(no)007:18: bdag nyida rab 'byams rgyal ba'i spyi gzugs bla ma
NK132(no)007:19: rina po che khyed mkhyen no //
NK132(no)007:20: las ngan pa'i sems can skyabs dang skyob pa mgona
NK132(no)007:21: dang dpung gnyen meda pa bdag la thugsa brtse ba
NK132(no)007:22: chen pos rjes su bzung la spyan gyis gzigas shig
NK132(no)007:23: ces gsol ba'o // blang dor gyi gnas mi shes
NK132(no)007:24: pa'i ma rig pa'i mun pa 'thiba posa nona pa
NK132(no)007:25: ces gsol ba'o // bdag ni / 'akhara bar skye
NK132(no)007:26: ba'i tsha thoga ma meda pa nas lus ngag yid
NK132(no)007:27: gsum gyi mi dge ba'i lasa dang /
NK132(no)007:28: nyon mongs dug lnga dug gsum sogs kyis sdig pa
NK132(no)007:29: mi dge ba'i tshogs dpag tu med pasa zil gyis
NK132(no)007:30: non pas / bka' drin can gyi bla ma dam
NK132(no)007:31: par lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgo nas brnyasa shinga
NK132(no)007:32: non pas / / bla ma gcig dang dkyil 'khor
NK132(no)007:33: gcig la brten pa'i rdo rje'i spun la khong khros
NK132(no)007:34: non pas / / pa dang / gsang sngags kyi
NK132(no)007:35: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshiga nyams pa
NK132(no)007:36: non pas / / pa dang / dang / so
NK132(no)007:37: thar gyi ltung ba sde lnga sogs kyi sdom pa
NK132(no)007:38: non pas / / pa dang / dang / nyams
NK132(no)007:39: pa dang / byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa'i gansa
NK132(no)007:40: kun la yanga 'gal ba'i nyesa spyod mi dge ba
NK132(no)007:41: chen po' gayanga sara lhung bas nyes pa'i tshogs ma
NK132(no)007:42: non pas / / pa dang / dang / nyams
NK132(no)007:43: pa dang / gus pa dang / ma 'atshala bzhina
NK132(no)007:44: du nongsa pa kun phyis su mi 'gyangs bar da
NK132(no)007:45: ring nyid nas shin tu gnonga 'gyoda drag po'i sems
NK132(no)007:47: byang zhing 'dag par mdzad du gsol /
NK132(no)007:48: tshe rabs sngona chada bla ma dkon mchog gsum khyed
NK132(no)007:49: kyi bka'a bstsal ba las 'adsa pa'i nyes tshogs rgya
NK132(no)007:50: mtsho chen po de lta bu' sdig pa dang ltung
NK132(no)007:51: ba ma byang bar tshe 'di nas 'jig rten pha
NK132(no)007:52: rol tu songa bar gyur na ni /
NK132(no)007:53: bdag sogs dmyal ba mnar med du lhung nas 'bar
NK132(no)007:54: ba'i ma shin tu bzoda daka'a bas ngesa para du
NK132(no)007:55: bsrega pa na / da tshe bdag nyida thugs rje
NK132(no)007:56: chen pos 'dora phoda dama ste mi phod ces so
NK132(no)007:57: bsrega pa na / // gnyis pa ni /
NK132(no)007:58: tshe rabs 'khor ba thog ma dang matha'a ma meda pa' khams gsum 'khor bar 'khrul ba'i gzhi na /
NK132(no)007:59: rig pa rtsal gyi shes rab des ngo ma shes
NK132(no)007:60: shing sems phra ba de shes rab kyi ngo bor
NK132(no)007:61: yang ma skyes pas lung ma bstana gya chos nyida
NK132(no)007:62: nas 'khrul te / 'khrul gzhi thams cad kyi rtsa ba 'di la thug pa yin te /
NK132(no)007:64: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa //
NK132(no)007:65: shes pa dran med yengs pa yin //
NK132(no)007:66: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pa //
NK132(no)007:67: bdag gzhan gnyis su 'dzin pa yin //
NK132(no)007:68: lhan skyes kun brtags ma rig gnyis //
NK132(no)007:69: sems can kun gyi 'khrul gzhi yin //
NK132(no)007:70: zhes gsungs pa bzhin kun 'byung lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK132(no)007:71: kun tu btags pa'i ma rig pa'i gdon chen po
NK132(no)007:72: dang 'grogas pa' rang bazhana skye gansa kyi bar do
NK132(no)007:73: la / theg pa chen po'i chosa kyi 'byor pa dang ldan zhing /
NK132(no)007:74: dal 'byor bco brgyad tshang ba'i mi lus rin po che thob nas /
NK132(no)007:75: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i bla ma dge ba'i bshes
NK132(no)007:76: gnyen mnyes pa gsum gyi sgo nas mnyesa par byed
NK132(no)007:77: cing / thos bsam sgoma pa'i shes rab la brtena
NK132(no)007:78: nas mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i ngesa 'byung dang
NK132(no)007:79: cing / / don gnyis ldan pa'i byang chub mchog tu semsa bskyed pa dang /
NK132(no)007:81: rgyal sras rnams kyis kun la bslab bya ste //
NK132(no)007:82: gtso bo pha rol phyin pa drug la bslab //
NK132(no)007:83: zhes gsungs pa bzhin phyin drug dang ldan pa'i theg
NK132(no)007:84: pa chen po'i lam mchoga tu gyur ba bsnyen para
NK132(no)007:86: gnyis pa 'chi kha'i bar do la gnyis /
NK132(no)007:87: rkyen ngan dang gnad gcod mi 'byung zhing rnam shes
NK132(no)007:88: rlung zhon gyi gdams pa la goms pas dbyings rig
NK132(no)007:90: rags pa dang phra ba'i thim rim rnams 'char dus gdams ngag dran nas ngo shes par smon pa'o //
NK132(no)007:93: dus kyi nyen te rgyal po 'gro gyur na //
NK132(no)007:95: dus kyi nyen te 'jig rten pha rol tu 'gro
NK132(no)007:96: ba la 'chi kha ma'i bar do zhes bya ste
NK132(no)007:97: / de'i tshe na rang gis rang gsod pa dang /
NK132(no)007:98: g.yang du mchongs ba dang 'gag grir 'chi ba sogs 'chi rkyen ngan pa dang /
NK132(no)007:99: 'chi kha ganda gcoda kyi sdug bsngal drag po mi 'byung zhing bde bar 'chi ba de'i tshe /
NK132(no)007:100: chos kyi dbyingsa dang rang gi rig pa dbyer med
NK132(no)007:101: du bsra ba yisa 'od gasla sbubsa 'jug gi gdams
NK132(no)007:102: pa mngona du gyur nas gadda ma'i gzhi'am 'chi srid
NK132(no)007:103: chos sku'i 'od gsal la grol bar shog cig ces
NK132(no)007:104: smon pa'o // gal te tshe 'dir ka dag rdzogs pa chen po la gomas pa'i stobsa chung na /
NK132(no)007:106: sgo brgyad 'khor ba'i skar khung can //
NK132(no)007:107: sgo gcig phyag rgya chen po'i sgo //
NK132(no)007:108: zhes gsungs pa ltar lte ba mtshog ma sna rna
NK132(no)007:109: ba mig gshang lam chu lam kha ste ma dag
NK132(no)007:110: 'khor ba'i sgo brgyad po bakaga nasa sgo gcig phyag
NK132(no)007:111: rgya chen po'i sgo ste spyi bo tshangas pa'i bu
NK132(no)007:113: rnam shesa rlung zhon gyi gdamsa pa yisa rab chos sku lta ba rgyas 'debs kyi 'pho ba'am /
NK132(no)007:114: khregs chod rang lam gyi gronga 'pho gronga 'jug gi
NK132(no)007:115: 'pho ba la brtena nas mkha'a la spyoda pa'i rig
NK132(no)007:116: pa 'dzina pa'i gansa thob par shog cig ces smon
NK132(no)007:117: pa'o // de ltar yang bar do'i smon lam thar pa'i lcags kyu las /
NK132(no)007:118: de la mi gnas rnam shes 'pho ba na //
NK132(no)007:119: lte ba smin mtshams mtshog ma sna rna ba //
NK132(no)007:120: mig dang gshang lam chu lam kha dang dgu //
NK132(no)007:121: bkag nas sgo gcig dbye bar byin gyis rlobs //
NK132(no)007:122: 'dod gzugs gzugs med gnod sbyin mi'am ci //
NK132(no)007:123: mi dang dud 'gro dmyal ba yi dwags su //
NK132(no)007:124: skye ba'i skye sgo bkag nas mkha' spyod du //
NK132(no)007:125: dpa' bo mkha' 'gros bsu bar byin gyis rlobs //
NK132(no)007:128: sgo dgu 'khor ba'i skar khung can //
NK132(no)007:129: sgo gcig phyag rgya chen po'i sgo //
NK132(no)007:130: sgo dgu bcad nas sgo gcig phye //
NK132(no)007:131: thar pa'i lam la the mi tshom //
NK132(no)007:132: zhes gsungs pa rnams dang bu ga'i dbye bsdu tsam las don gyi gnad gcig go //
NK132(no)007:133: gong du bshad pa de ltara byang chub semas dapa'a
NK132(no)007:134: yi grong 'pho grong 'jug sogs kyi 'pho ba'i lugsa
NK132(no)007:135: mngona du ma gyur na ni /
NK132(no)007:137: sa ni sa la rang thim nas //
NK132(no)007:138: lus ni lci zhing ldang mi nus //
NK132(no)007:139: langs nas 'gro ba'i stobs kun zad //
NK132(no)007:140: chu ni chu la thim pa'i tshe //
NK132(no)007:141: kha chu sna chu 'dzag par byed //
NK132(no)007:142: de bzhin me la me thim pas //
NK132(no)007:143: kha sna dag ni rab tu skam //
NK132(no)007:144: lus kyi mtha' yi drod rnams 'chor //
NK132(no)007:145: de bzhin rlung la rlung thim pas //
NK132(no)007:146: dbugs ni ngar ngar yan lag 'phra //
NK132(no)007:147: mig kyang gyen la ldog pa'o //
NK132(no)007:148: rtags ni su la 'byung ba ste //
NK132(no)007:150: zhes gsungs pa ltar sa la sa thim pa'i rtags su lus lci zhing ldang mi nus pa dang /
NK132(no)007:151: chu la chu thim pa'i rtags su kha sna nas chu 'dzag pa dang /
NK132(no)007:152: me la ma thim pa'i rtags su kha sna'i chu skama zhing gshin dri bro ba dang /
NK132(no)007:153: rlunga la rlung thim pa'i rtags su dbugsa ngar zhing
NK132(no)007:154: yan lag 'jag skya tsam phra ba'i snang ba 'char
NK132(no)007:155: zhing mig sprina gyen du ldog pa ste /
NK132(no)007:157: bred sha thob pa'i mig bgrad nas //
NK132(no)007:160: de nas lus kyi khrag 'dus nas //
NK132(no)007:161: srog rtsa'i nang nas khrag thig rgyab //
NK132(no)007:162: kha dang mig gnyis skya log 'gro //
NK132(no)007:163: dbugs ni khru gang tsam du chad //
NK132(no)007:165: de'i tshe phyi rtags su du ba lta bu dang /
NK132(no)007:167: srin bu ma khyer lta bu dang /
NK132(no)007:169: me 'abra ba lta bu'i snang ba 'char zhing /
NK132(no)007:171: 'degs byed don gyi rlung bros pas //
NK132(no)007:172: lus ni mi theg sgyid pa sgyur //
NK132(no)007:173: yan lag mi 'dus smra bar dka' //
NK132(no)007:174: mig ldog dbugs ni phyi ru 'phul //
NK132(no)007:175: bkrag mdangs bskyed pa'i rlung bros pas //
NK132(no)007:176: lus rnams kha sna bal dud chags //
NK132(no)007:177: sha tsha kha sna gshin dri snom //
NK132(no)007:178: dwangs snyigs 'byed pa'i rlung bros pas //
NK132(no)007:179: bza' btung mi len lus stobs 'chor //
NK132(no)007:180: me dang mnyam pa'i rlung bros pas //
NK132(no)007:181: lus kyi drod ni mtha' nas 'chor //
NK132(no)007:182: lus kyi bkrag dang gzi mdangs nyams //
NK132(no)007:183: bskal pa lus kyi rlung bros pas //
NK132(no)007:184: lus la za zi phyed phyed mang //
NK132(no)007:185: rtsa phran khrag ni srog rtsar 'dus //
NK132(no)007:186: zhes gsungs pa ltar rlung lnga bros pa'i byed las
NK132(no)007:187: kyis khyab bya sa chu me rlung nam mkha' ste
NK132(no)007:189: khyab byed ye shes thig le'i dpyid dpal te 'dir
NK132(no)007:190: sems dang rig pa mthar thug gi rgyab gyes pa
NK132(no)007:191: yin te / yul lnga 'dzin pa'i shes pa yada shes la thim para phyogsa pa'i tshe /
NK132(no)007:192: tshe 'di'i snang ba la zhen pa dang chagas pa
NK132(no)007:193: gdung ba rnams mi skye zhing bla ma'i gsungs pa'i
NK132(no)007:194: gdamsa ngaga rnams drana para shog cig ces smon pa'o
NK132(no)007:196: ragsa pa gdos bcas kyi phung po'i rtsa dang /
NK132(no)007:198: rlung gsuma gyi tshogsa pa so sor gyes pa' rten
NK132(no)007:199: 'brala gyi mthu lasa shin tu phra ba snang ba
NK132(no)007:201: thob pa gsum gya thim rim rnams rim par 'char tshul ni /
NK132(no)007:202: skad cig dang por spyi bo nas pha las thob pa'i thig le dakara cha thur du babsa te /
NK132(no)007:203: nang rtags su snying stobsa lasa byung ba'i 'doda chagas
NK132(no)007:204: kyi rtog pa bzhi bcu 'aggas pa dang lhan cig
NK132(no)007:205: par rnama par shesa pa snang ba la thima pa
NK132(no)007:206: zhes bya ste / de'i tshe phyi rtags su stona
NK132(no)007:207: ganma g.ya' dag pa la zla 'oda kyis slong ba
NK132(no)007:209: gsang ba'i rtags su sems can la bde nyams tsam
NK132(no)007:210: dang rnal 'byor pa la bde nyams kyis brgyan pa'i
NK132(no)007:211: 'od gsal 'char ba de ranga ngo shes para shog
NK132(no)007:212: ces dang / skad cig gnyis pa la da bzhina
NK132(no)007:213: du lte ba nas ma las thob pa'i rak+ta damra
NK132(no)007:215: nang rtags su rdul lasa byung ba' zhe sdang gi rtog pa so gsum 'agga /
NK132(no)007:216: de ni snang ba de nyid mcheda pa la thim pa zhes bya /
NK132(no)007:217: phyi rtags su skara khung nyi zhur gyis slong ba lta bu'i damra lam 'char /
NK132(no)007:218: gsang ba'i rtags su sems can la gsal nyams tsam
NK132(no)007:219: dang rnal 'byor pa la des brgyan pa'i 'od gsal
NK132(no)007:220: 'char ba de rang nga shes para shoga cig ces
NK132(no)007:221: dang / skad cig gsum pa la de nas khu
NK132(no)007:222: rdul gnyis snyanga gara 'phrada cing zhal 'dzom pa lasa
NK132(no)007:223: dang / / nang rtags su mun pa can lasa
NK132(no)007:224: byung ba'i gata mug gi rtog pa bdun 'agga par
NK132(no)007:225: 'gyur zhing de'i tshe mcheda pa de nyera thob la
NK132(no)007:227: phyi rtags su ston ganma g.ya' dag pa la smag gisa slong ba lta bu'i nag lam 'char /
NK132(no)007:228: gsang rtags su sems can la mi rtog pa'i nyams
NK132(no)007:229: tsam dang rnal 'byor pa la des brgyan pa'i 'od
NK132(no)007:230: gsal shar nas de'i ngang du brgyal ba la phyogsa
NK132(no)007:231: pa'i tshe / rtsol bral rang bzhag gi dran pa'am
NK132(no)007:232: drana pa'i mchog rgyal po sgrona me lta bu yis
NK132(no)007:233: zin nas nyera thoba 'oda gasla la chu dang chu
NK132(no)007:234: bzhin dbyer med du 'dresa nas mthar phyin gdoda ma'i
NK132(no)007:235: gzhi dbyingsa su sangsa rgyas par shog cig ces smon
NK132(no)007:236: pa'i tshe / pa ste / de ni 'chi kha'i
NK132(no)007:237: bar do mi gsal bar gsal 'debs pa sgeg mos
NK132(no)007:238: me long la blta ba ltar dran pa'i gdams pa'o
NK132(no)007:239: pa'i tshe / pa ste / // gal te chos
NK132(no)007:240: nyid kyi dran pa' stobsa zhan pasa ma zin nas
NK132(no)007:241: pa'i tshe / pa ste / // brgyal te /
NK132(no)007:242: semsa meda pa'i skabsa lta bur gyur na dal gcig
NK132(no)007:243: brgyal nas de nas skad cig bzhi pa la thig
NK132(no)007:244: le gnyis kha phyes te rtog tshogs brgyad cu 'gag
NK132(no)007:246: brten pa bag chags dang bcas pa dag ste chosa
NK132(no)007:247: dbyingsa spros bral gyi ngang la sada nas rig pa
NK132(no)007:248: dwangsa gasla rtog pa meda pa mngon du gyur ba
NK132(no)007:250: 'acha ba chos sku'i 'od gasla mngona du gyur bar shog cig ces smon pa'o //
NK132(no)007:251: da ltara 'chi ba chos sku'i rnal 'byor dang bsre
NK132(no)007:252: ba yisa gdod ma gzhi'i nanga dbyingsa su btsan sa
NK132(no)007:253: ma zin na / shin tu phra ba'i rlung semsa kyi cha slar yang lugsa ldog tu langs te /
NK132(no)007:254: lugs ldog ces ci la zer na ma h+aa yo
NK132(no)007:255: ga'i skabs su 'od gsal ldog pa can zhes 'od
NK132(no)007:256: gsal de shar nas rtog tshogs brgyad cu 'gag kyang
NK132(no)007:257: 'od gsal ngos ma zin na slar yang 'khrul bas
NK132(no)007:259: de yang nye bar thoba pa langs pa las gti mug gi rtog pa bdun dang /
NK132(no)007:260: mcheda pa langs pa las zhe sdang gi rtog pa so gsum dang /
NK132(no)007:261: snanga ba langs pa las 'dod chags kyi rtog pa
NK132(no)007:262: bzhi bcu rnams langs nas slar yang 'khrul ba yin
NK132(no)007:263: no // de'i phyir chos nyid kyi bar do gdod
NK132(no)007:264: ma'i gzhi dbyingsa ka dag gi klong chen po de
NK132(no)007:265: khregas choda kyi lta ba tshe 'dir yang yang goms
NK132(no)007:266: pa'i stobs kyis mngona du gyur cing grol bar shog
NK132(no)007:268: de ni ka dag gi grol sa yin la de
NK132(no)007:269: ngo shes na de phan chad kyi snang ba gang
NK132(no)007:271: ngo ma shes na lhun grub kyi snang ba /
NK132(no)007:273: ye shes bzhi sbyor gyi snang ba /
NK132(no)007:274: gzhi snang chen po'i snang ba dang bzhi rim pa bzhin du shar ba 'chad 'gyur ltar ro //
NK132(no)007:275: gsum pa chos nyid bar do ni /
NK132(no)007:276: de ltar gzhi dbyings ka dag chen po ngos ma
NK132(no)007:277: zin nas gazha snanga yana lugsa kyi 'oda gasla shar
NK132(no)007:278: ba na / lhun grub kyi snang ba shar ba
NK132(no)007:279: de'i tshe dus ma 'gyur bar snang ba 'gyur nas
NK132(no)007:280: phyi sa rdo ri brag gi snang ba ni nub
NK132(no)007:281: ba na / / rang gi spyod yul du gyur
NK132(no)007:282: ba'i snanga ba thamsa cad 'oda zer lnga ru snang
NK132(no)007:283: ba na / / ste / gang du bltas kyang
NK132(no)007:284: za 'og bkrama pa ltar snang ba thams cad shin
NK132(no)007:285: tu bkra ba kha dog sna tshogs pa /
NK132(no)007:286: phyi nang dang yangs dog med pa 'gul 'phrig gi
NK132(no)007:287: rnam pa can rab tu 'tsher bar shar ba'i tshe
NK132(no)007:288: / da lta thoda rgala la ci tsam gomas pa'i
NK132(no)007:289: nyara rgyu lasa rig pa'i grogs su grol long yod
NK132(no)007:290: par 'char la skad cig dang po la rang snanga
NK132(no)007:291: rang bzhin meda para shes nas yid ches /
NK132(no)007:293: gsum par grol thog tu btsan sa zin nas de
NK132(no)007:294: phan chad kyi snang ba gang yang mi 'byung bas
NK132(no)007:295: chosa nyada ciga char zada para shog ces smon pa'o
NK132(no)007:296: // de nas gal te 'od gasla zung 'jug la
NK132(no)007:297: thim nas zhi khro rigsa brgya'i snang ba rang shara
NK132(no)007:298: // te / sku de dag kyang mi che ba
NK132(no)007:299: mi chung ba cha mnyam pa rgyan dang kha dog
NK132(no)007:300: dang bzhugs tshul dang gdan khri dang rang rang gi
NK132(no)007:301: phyag rgya dang bcas par 'char zhing /
NK132(no)007:302: de'i tshe 'brug stong ldir ba lta bu'i sgra yis 'jigas shinga /
NK132(no)007:303: mtshon cha'i rnam par zug pa'i zer gyis sngangs /
NK132(no)007:304: sku che ba 'jig rten gyi khams khyab pa lta bu yi snang basa skrag par gyur ba na /
NK132(no)007:305: de la senga ge'i gsoba mthong ba ltara matshanga phug
NK132(no)007:306: rigs nas rang snang la bag ma tsha ba'i gdenga
NK132(no)007:307: thob par shoga ces smon pa'o //
NK132(no)007:308: de la bsam gatana gyi zhag ni da lta ting
NK132(no)007:309: nge 'dzin la ci tsam gnas pa'i yun ring thung
NK132(no)007:310: la gsungs pas / bshad rgyud las /
NK132(no)007:311: 'od gsal snang ba dus gcig shar //
NK132(no)007:312: rtogs pa'i shes rab rim gyis skye zhes /
NK132(no)007:313: tshom bu dang bzhi sbyor yang gcig char 'char gsungs /
NK132(no)007:314: snang ba rnams la shes pa mi 'gyur bar rang
NK132(no)007:315: snang du shes thog tu ce re mnyam par bzhag
NK132(no)007:316: dgos gsungs / da lta 'od gsal gyi snang ba
NK132(no)007:317: lug rgyud dang bcas pa'i gdangs ngos zin zhing de
NK132(no)007:318: la goms nas 'di las phyir tha mal du mi
NK132(no)007:319: ldog pa thod rgal goms pa las yin pas 'di
NK132(no)007:320: dgos gsungs / gces so // des na 'dir sngar
NK132(no)007:321: gyi lu gu rgyud thig le dang bcas pa kun
NK132(no)007:322: smin pas dngos su lug rgyud mi snang ngo gsungs
NK132(no)007:323: dgos gsungs / gces so // so // de'i zhag
NK132(no)007:324: dang po la rnam par snang mdzad rang snang gi
NK132(no)007:326: gnyis par mi bskyod rdo rje /
NK132(no)007:328: bzhi par snang ba mtha' yas /
NK132(no)007:329: lnga pa la don yod grub pa rang snang gi
NK132(no)007:330: tshom bu dang bcas pa 'char zhing rgyal ba rigsa
NK132(no)007:332: ranga gi snying ga nas 'oda shin tu phra ba zhig 'char te /
NK132(no)007:333: de sku thams cad kyi thugs ka dang 'brela bar
NK132(no)007:334: 'char ba yisa rig pa 'ada gasal la 'jug pa
NK132(no)007:336: de nas rang gi snying ga nas 'od thag tshon skud sgril ba tsam zhig 'char te /
NK132(no)007:337: sku de yang ranga gi lus la thim pa'i snang
NK132(no)007:338: ba 'char ba yasa 'ada gasla rig pa la tshur
NK132(no)007:340: de'i tshe rang snang la yid ches pa ma panga
NK132(no)007:341: du bu 'jug pa lta bur grola bar shog ces
NK132(no)007:342: smon pa'o // de bazhana du zung 'jug zung 'jug
NK132(no)007:343: gi don ni rig pa'i rang 'od lhug par shar
NK132(no)007:344: smon pa'o // ba de dang / chos nyid ma'i
NK132(no)007:345: 'od gsal lnga longs sku'i zhing snang ye nas lam
NK132(no)007:346: snang du yod pa gnyis rig pa'i ngo kha la
NK132(no)007:347: dus 'dzom pas rig thog tu dbyer med gcig tu
NK132(no)007:348: smon pa'o // ba de dang / 'jug pa'o //
NK132(no)007:349: ye shesa la thim pasa rang gi snying ga nas
NK132(no)007:350: 'oda zer sna lnga shar bas dbang po'i yul du
NK132(no)007:351: snang tshad khyab pa snam bu'i tshul te /
NK132(no)007:352: dper na mthing ga'i snam bu'i steng du thig le
NK132(no)007:353: lnga'i zer dang ldan pa me long kha sbubs pa
NK132(no)007:354: lta bu cana 'char ba de la ya shesa bazha
NK132(no)007:355: sbyor gyi snanga ba zhes bya ba ste /
NK132(no)007:356: de na rdo rje semsa dpa'i khonga senga gi lam zhes bya'o //
NK132(no)007:357: de ltar snanga ba'i tshe na mi 'gyur ba gser
NK132(no)007:358: gyi thur ma lta bu'i thabs mchog tu dran pas
NK132(no)007:359: rig pa rang sa las ma g.yos pa'i ngang la
NK132(no)007:360: btsan sa zana te grol bar shog cig ces smon
NK132(no)007:361: pa'o // de nas ye shesa lhun grub la thim pasa /
NK132(no)007:362: sku ltar shar bas snang ba gang du'ang mi 'byed pa dang /
NK132(no)007:363: ye shesa ltar shar bas snang ba zang thal /
NK132(no)007:364: thugsa rja ltar shar bas snying rje'i shugs 'khor ba
NK132(no)007:365: la 'jug /'oda ltar shar bas snang cha nang na
NK132(no)007:366: gsal / matha'a grala ltar shar bas ngo bo nyid du sangs /
NK132(no)007:367: gnyisa meda ltar shar bas shes pa rtse gcig tu gnas /
NK132(no)007:368: dag pa ltar shar bas ye shes ma bu 'brel /
NK132(no)007:369: ma dag pa ltar shar bas srid pa'i 'byung khungs ma 'gags pa'o /
NK132(no)007:370: de'i tshe grol ba gnad kyi man ngag gsum ni /
NK132(no)007:371: ma pang du bu 'jug pa lta bu'i man ngag
NK132(no)007:372: sngar 'dris kyi mi dang 'phrad pa ltar rang snang
NK132(no)007:373: la the tshom mi za bar 1yid ches /
NK132(no)007:374: mi 'gyur ba gser gyi thur ma'i 2dpes yid ches
NK132(no)007:375: de las gzhan du mi yengs par btsan sa bzung
NK132(no)007:376: / dpag chen gyi 3mda' tshur la mi ldog pa'i
NK132(no)007:377: dpes gshis la mi g.yo bar bzhag pas grol ba
NK132(no)007:378: / yin no // de ltar lhun grub ya shesa
NK132(no)007:379: chen po'i sgo 'char lugs brgyad du shara bar bstan
NK132(no)007:380: pa de yang 'akhara 'das kya 'jug ldog rig pa
NK132(no)007:382: rig pa'i rang rtsala tsam du shara ba yang rig
NK132(no)007:383: pa ye gdod ma nyid nas gazha lasa ma g.yosa
NK132(no)007:385: gzhi snanga chena para yida chasa par shog ces smon pa'o //
NK132(no)007:386: da yanga chos 'di'i sgo nas chos nyid dag pa'i
NK132(no)007:387: bar dor grol ba'i gdengs dang gdams ngag med cing
NK132(no)007:388: rnal 'byor chen po'i bskyed rdzogs kyi rim pa la
NK132(no)007:390: rlung semsa kyi rang bzhin tsam gya lus de nyid /
NK132(no)007:391: bar dor matshana dapa rdzagas par brgyan pa'i ya dam
NK132(no)007:392: gyi lha' skur mngona par byang ba lngas chub pa'i
NK132(no)007:393: rang bzhin bar do longsa spyod rdzogs pa'i sku' snang
NK132(no)007:394: ba 'char ba dang bsre ba yasa sgyu ma lta
NK132(no)007:395: bu'i yi dam gyi lha'i sku ru ldang bar shog
NK132(no)007:397: de yang rang snang longs skur shar ba'i dbyings su
NK132(no)007:398: 'tshang rgya ba'i chos nyid dag pa'i bar do dang
NK132(no)007:399: / snang ba rang mtshan par 'dzin pa bar do
NK132(no)007:400: sgyu lus chos skur ldang ba'i dod thub bstan pa
NK132(no)007:403: chos nyid dag pa'i bar do dang //
NK132(no)007:404: yi dam lha yi sgyu lus gnyis //
NK132(no)007:407: yang gang zag ganga zhig mosa pasa spyod pa rnams
NK132(no)007:408: kyang skabs 'dir rjes dran lnga dang mangna shasa drug
NK132(no)007:409: dang ma brjed pa'i gzungsa sogs kyis dbugsa 'byin nas
NK132(no)007:411: 'di'i skabs sngon nas shes pa'i bsod nams khyad par can gyis rang snang du /
NK132(no)007:413: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad steng gi nam mkhar byon nas dbang bskur ba dang /
NK132(no)007:414: bla ma dran ma thag nam mkhar byon nas gdams
NK132(no)007:415: pa ngo 'phrod pa 'byung bas mi grol mi srid
NK132(no)007:416: de / yi dam la mos pa rnams lhas lung ston /
NK132(no)007:417: de gnyis gcig tu 'dren pa ni lha'i mchog bla ma yin pas so //
NK132(no)007:418: bla ma mchog la gdung ba dang ldan pa rnams
NK132(no)007:419: mos gus kyis dran pa'i mod la mdun du byon
NK132(no)007:420: nas man ngag bstan cing rjes su 'dzin par shog
NK132(no)007:421: cig ces dang / bskyed rim la goms pa rnams yi dam rjes su dran nas zhal mthonga zhing /
NK132(no)007:422: lta ba rjes su dran nas sngar 'dris pa'i mi
NK132(no)007:423: phyis 'phrad pa tsam gyis ngo shes pa lta bu
NK132(no)007:424: dang ni / bsam gatana rnams rjes su dran pas zhag lngar bsam gtan la gnas pa dang /
NK132(no)007:425: skya gansa rjes su dran pa'i dbang po tha ma
NK132(no)007:426: rnams rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing khams su dbugs 'byin
NK132(no)007:427: pa dang / bla ma'i mana ngaga rjes su dran
NK132(no)007:428: pas rang gi snang ba rnams dang gnyis su med
NK132(no)007:429: par spyod pa dang de rnams drana para shoga cig
NK132(no)007:430: pa dang / ces dang / de bzhina du sngona gyi skye gansa shes pa dang /
NK132(no)007:431: 'chi 'apha ba dang na skye ba shesa pa dang /
NK132(no)007:432: pha rola gya ni semas shes pa dang /
NK132(no)007:433: snang ba lkoga tu gyura pa thams cad shesa pa dang /
NK132(no)007:434: rigsa drug gi gansa ragas mathanga zhing shasa pa dang /
NK132(no)007:435: dabnga pa rnams rnama par dag pa'i mngona par shesa pa dang drug 'char ste /
NK132(no)007:437: rigs kyi bu de la mngon par shes pa drug 'char te /
NK132(no)007:438: sngon gyi skye gnas shes pa dang /
NK132(no)007:439: 'chi 'pho dang skye ba shes pa dang /
NK132(no)007:440: pha rol gyi sems shes pa dang /
NK132(no)007:441: snang ba lkog tu gyur pa thams cad shes pa dang /
NK132(no)007:442: rigs drug gi gnas mthong zhing shes pa dang /
NK132(no)007:443: dbang po rnams rnam par dag pa'i mngona par shesa pa drug 'char ro //
NK132(no)007:445: de bzhin du sngona chada thosa sa cog gisa mtshona
NK132(no)007:446: pa'i chosa kyi rnam grangas tshad meda pa rang rgyud
NK132(no)007:447: la 'achara ba'i mi brjed pa'i gzungas thoba pa'i tshe
NK132(no)007:448: / de dag tu ngesa para grola bar byed pa'i
NK132(no)007:449: ganda rig pa stong nyid spros brala zang thal bsam
NK132(no)007:450: brjod las 'das pa de ka daga ga rang ngor
NK132(no)007:451: 'dug pas mthar thug gi grol sa rig pa cera
NK132(no)007:452: mathanga yin par rang thog tu ngo shes /
NK132(no)007:454: grol thog tu gdenga thoba par shoga cig ces smon pa'o //
NK132(no)007:455: madra na chosa nyada bar ma da'i snang tshul la
NK132(no)007:456: phar rnama para dpyada na matha'a meda pa zhig yin
NK132(no)007:457: kyanga / dpyoda makhana gyi shes pa nyida la tshur brtagas pa na /
NK132(no)007:458: ganga du'nga grub pa meda pa la /
NK132(no)007:459: meda da snyam pa'i 'dzin pa'ang rang sar grola ba /
NK132(no)007:460: skad cig ma rjen pa'i rang ngo rtog dpyod med
NK132(no)007:461: pa 'ad na gadda ma' grola sa par gyis btab
NK132(no)007:463: thugs rje yul la ji ltar 'jug cing de nyid kyi rjes mi bcad /
NK132(no)007:464: nang du mi dgag par shar ba de kar cog
NK132(no)007:465: gis bzhag pas phyi nang bar med kyi shes pa
NK132(no)007:466: zang thal le bas bar do'i snang ba rig gdangs
NK132(no)007:468: grol sa cer mthong du ngo shes pas shel 'od
NK132(no)007:469: nang du nub pa ltar gzhona nu bum pa'i sku
NK132(no)007:470: thoba nasa nang gsal thim la ma rmugs pa'i ngang
NK132(no)007:471: du gnas kyang / slar yang lhun grub kyi rtsal
NK132(no)007:472: lasa sku dang zhing khams rgyan dang bkod pa du
NK132(no)007:474: 'gra ba'i dana du ji srid 'akhara ba ma stong
NK132(no)007:475: bar du bzhugs te dong nas sprug nus par shog
NK132(no)007:477: bzhi pa srid pa bar do bshad pa la /
NK132(no)007:478: srid pa bar do'i rang bzhin bshad pa /
NK132(no)007:479: rnam grol dbugs chen 'byin pa'i zhing khams lnga la bgrod par smon pa /
NK132(no)007:480: dbang po tha ma'i tha ma rnams pha ma chos
NK132(no)007:481: ldan gyi rgyud du skyes nas skye 'chi bar do
NK132(no)007:482: gsum gang rung du grol bar smon pas mjug bsdu
NK132(no)007:484: de ltar chos nyid bar dor ma grol nas gala
NK132(no)007:485: ta srida pa bar do la yang nas yang du
NK132(no)007:486: kha 'khyal cing / tshor ba 'du shes 'du byed
NK132(no)007:487: rnam shes te minga bazha 'dus pa can gyi phung
NK132(no)007:488: kha 'khyal cing / po / mig sogs dabnga pa kun tshanga ba yid kya lus su grub pa /
NK132(no)007:489: shi bar ngo shesa shing sngar las drana pa bdun 'gyur gyis gasla ba /
NK132(no)007:490: rnam par grola ba'i sa dang 'gro drug gi skye gansa gang rung la thogas pa ste /
NK132(no)007:492: de la slob dpon phal dag rdo rje gdan rgya gar gyi de la ngos 'dzin yang /
NK132(no)007:493: 'dir ka dag mi 'gyur ba'i nang dbyings sangs rgyas
NK132(no)007:494: thams cad sangs rgya ba'i gnas mchog dag pa mya
NK132(no)007:495: ngan las 'das pa'i sgor zhugs pa de yin la
NK132(no)007:497: dper na r+ts+was ni me 'dzin dang //
NK132(no)007:500: sa khung bris pa'i snyis 'dzin no //
NK132(no)007:502: ma'i mngal ni ma dag pa 'khor ba'i sgo 'gro
NK132(no)007:503: drug gi skye gnas gang rung la 'dod pa yin
NK132(no)007:504: pas sgra ji bzhin ma yin par shes par bya'o
NK132(no)007:505: // gang du'ang rang sa mi zin pa bya sgra
NK132(no)007:506: rlung gis khyer ba lta bur lasa kyi rlung gi
NK132(no)007:507: rjesa su 'gro bas nyam thaga cing /
NK132(no)007:508: breda sngangas dang bcas pa'i sdug bsngal gyis gdung ba /
NK132(no)007:509: zhag bdun tshana re re' matshamas su skye 'acha'i snang
NK132(no)007:510: ba re re shar ba'i sdug bsngal gyi tshara ba
NK132(no)007:511: nyamas su myanga ste skye gansa 'tshol ba'o //
NK132(no)007:512: de'i phyir dge ba'i stobs 'degs pa la'ang bdun tshig phan yon che ba yin no //
NK132(no)007:514: a ti bkod pa chen po las //
NK132(no)007:515: dpal dang ldan dang pad+ma brtsegs pa dang //
NK132(no)007:516: las rab nyid ni yongs su rdzogs pa'i zhing //
NK132(no)007:517: rin chen 'byung ldan pad+ma gar dbang rta //
NK132(no)007:518: don yod grub pas shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyong //
NK132(no)007:519: dkar ser dmar dang ljang gu'i kha dog gsal //
NK132(no)007:521: dus de'i tshe rang bzhin sprul pa'i sku'i zhing khams mngona para dag'a ba dang /
NK132(no)007:525: dbus phyogsa dur khrod me ra 'abra ba ste /
NK132(no)007:526: rnama grala dbugas chena 'byin pa lnga'i dag pa'i zhanga
NK132(no)007:527: khams rnams yang yang yada la gomas par byas nasa
NK132(no)007:528: der 'dun pa gtad pa'i mthus zhing de dag rnams
NK132(no)007:529: su gdon ma za bar bgroda nus para shoga cig
NK132(no)007:530: ces smon pa'o // yang de nyid las /
NK132(no)007:531: skal ldan stobs med snying po'i don 'dzin pa //
NK132(no)007:532: der ni dbugs dbyung skye ba gcig pa ste //
NK132(no)007:533: lnga brgya dag na nges pa'i sar grol lo //
NK132(no)007:535: zhing gang du skye ba der rgyud smin nas mdun
NK132(no)007:536: gyi nam mkhar mi mjed brtsegs pa la khro bo'i
NK132(no)007:537: zhing mthong dus de'i byin rlabs kyis shes sgrib dag
NK132(no)007:538: nas ka dag gi sar byang chub pa'o zhes gsungs
NK132(no)007:540: gal te rig pa rtsal gyi dabnga gasa rgyud ma
NK132(no)007:541: smin zhing chos nyid kyi badna pa ma mathanga na
NK132(no)007:542: rigsa drug so so'i gansa ragas mangna du gyur ram
NK132(no)007:543: dmyala ba sdonga dum lta bu dang ya dwagsa du
NK132(no)007:544: ba / de gnyis mag bo thur du lta ba /
NK132(no)007:546: lha mana kha chara bab pa lta bu mag bo'i lta phyogs yanga 'phrada /
NK132(no)007:547: lha ma gnyis kha dog dakara zhanga mgo bo yang gyena du 'grenga /
NK132(no)007:548: 'doda lha rigs drug yul la dag'a ba dang gdung ba skye ba dang /
NK132(no)007:549: gzugsa khamsa su skye na 'ada la gdung ba dang
NK132(no)007:550: gzugsa med na nam mkha' rnam shes sogs ca yanga
NK132(no)007:551: mada pa'i stonga phyada la dag'a gdunga 'achara zhing /
NK132(no)007:552: khyad para du pha ma'i 'adu 'phrada mathanga ba'i tsha
NK132(no)007:553: de la chagas pa skye ba dang sdang ba mig
NK132(no)007:554: ser med par bden mada sgyu ma lta bur sbyong
NK132(no)007:555: ba'am / dbang gsum pa'i ye shes kyis dabnga don nyamas su myong zhing /
NK132(no)007:556: skye gansa rnam pa bzhi ya sbyang gazha dang sbyong byada la gomas pa'i bskyed rim gyis /
NK132(no)007:557: gsang sngagas rdo rje theg pa la spyod pa'i lus
NK132(no)007:558: rten can du skye ba sprul sku' rnal 'byor dang
NK132(no)007:559: bsre ba yis / pha ma chos ldan gyi mngal
NK132(no)007:560: du nyanga matshamas sbyor ba' mthu thoba par shog cig
NK132(no)007:561: bsre ba yis / ces smon pa'o // spros bcas
NK132(no)007:562: spros med shin tu spros med rab tu spros med
NK132(no)007:563: rnams kyi smin byed dabnga dang /
NK132(no)007:564: snyan brgyud man ngag zab mo'i grala byed kyi khrada dang /
NK132(no)007:565: srung du med pa gcig char ba'i bsrung bya dam
NK132(no)007:566: tshiga dang thaba bya 'brasa bu sku gsum dang rnama
NK132(no)007:567: pa bazha ru bsre ba dang /
NK132(no)007:568: sgo gsuma po snang ba lha grags pa sngagas dran
NK132(no)007:569: rtog chasa nyada du 'apha ba'i ganda la ma gomas
NK132(no)007:570: na 'byung ba bazha'i rlung gi byed lasa kyasa /
NK132(no)007:571: ri nyil ba rgya mtsho 'phyur ba nags tshal mes
NK132(no)007:572: bsreg pa dus matha'i rlung chen langs ba lta bu'i
NK132(no)007:573: shin tu 'ajagas pa' sgra bzhi dang /
NK132(no)007:574: dug gsuma lasa skyes pa'i 'dod chags kyi rang gzugs dkar lhang lhang /
NK132(no)007:575: zhe sdang gi rang gzugs dmar lam lam /
NK132(no)007:576: gti mug gi rang gzugs nag 'thum me ste gacanga rong gsum dang /
NK132(no)007:577: sngon bsags baga chagas las skyes pa'i gshin rje'i gshed ma' gzugsa sna tshogs dang /
NK132(no)007:578: ma chu gacana gazana sogs kyi mgo brnyan sna tshogs
NK132(no)007:579: pa shin tu 'jigas pa'i tshogsa dpag tu med pa
NK132(no)007:580: mthong ba'i tshe / bla ma dang dkona machaga gsuma la skyabsa su 'gra ba dang /
NK132(no)007:581: zag bcas dang zag med kyi dge ba'i ram zlas
NK132(no)007:582: dag pa'i zhing du dbugsa 'byin par shog cig ces
NK132(no)007:583: smon pa'o // de bzhin du dala 'byor bco brgyad
NK132(no)007:584: tshang ba' lus rten gya mangla sga ngan pa bkag
NK132(no)007:586: smon lam rnam par dag pas matshamas sbyar nasa /
NK132(no)007:587: matha rasa kyi yana tana bdun ldana gyi lus rtena
NK132(no)007:588: bzang po la brten nas bla ma mchog la mnyesa
NK132(no)007:589: pa gsum gyi sgo nas mnyes par byas nas /
NK132(no)007:590: theg pa chen po'i lam la tshul bzhin du spyod pa'i rang dbang thob pa dang /
NK132(no)007:591: bla ma dam pas ca gsunga gi bka'a bzhina du bsgrub pa yis /
NK132(no)007:592: mthar thug bla ma dang thugsa yid gciga tu 'drasa
NK132(no)007:593: te tshe de nyid la gdod ma'i gzhi dbyings su
NK132(no)007:594: grol bar shoga cig ces smon pa'o //
NK132(no)007:595: zhes bar do'i smon lam dgongs gcig rgya mtshos 'bru
NK132(no)007:596: 'brel gsal ba'i sgron me zhes bya ba 'di nyid
NK132(no)007:597: rang slob dam pa sprul pad+ma blo gros nas nan
NK132(no)007:598: gyis bskul bas dbu brtsams par /
NK132(no)007:599: slad nas mkhas btsun grub pa'i dbang phyug slob bu
NK132(no)007:600: 'jigs med phrin las kyis bskul bas kyang mtshams sbyar
NK132(no)007:601: te / sh+aakya'i dge slong thub bstan tshul khrims rgya
NK132(no)007:602: mtshos brgyud pa'i man ngag la brten nas bris pa'i
NK132(no)007:603: dge bas 'brel thogs sems can thams cad 'dren pa
NK132(no)007:604: 'od dpag med kyi zhing du skye ba'i rgyur gyur
NK132(no)007:605: te / cig // snyigs dus 'dir kun gyi lha
NK132(no)007:606: kha 'dre kha pho kha mo rkub la re ba
NK132(no)007:607: byed 'dug cing de bas 'di 'dra re blo thog
